<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Geriatrie Screening</title>
  <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">

  <script>
    if ('serviceWorker' in navigator) {
      navigator.serviceWorker.register('service-worker.js');
    }
  </script>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      margin: 1rem;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #111;
      max-width: 980px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: .3rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: .6rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 17px;
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: .5rem;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: .9rem;
    }

    .muted {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .stepper {
      display: flex;
      gap: .4rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 1.4rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .step-pill {
      padding: .45rem .7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #f0f0f0;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      font-size: 14px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .step-pill.active {
      background: #d0eaff;
      border-color: #8bbfe8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .page {
      display: none;
    }

    .page.active {
      display: block;
    }

    .card {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 700px) {
      .form-grid.two {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .form-grid.three {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: .25rem;
    }

    input[type="text"],
    input[type="date"],
    input[type="number"],
    select,
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding: .7rem;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #bbb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: white;
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 80px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .question-block {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: .9rem 0;
    }

    .question-block:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .question-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: .5rem;
    }

    .radio-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .7rem 1.2rem;
    }

    .radio-row label {
      font-weight: 400;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .35rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .radio-row input {
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }

    .test-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .test-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 17px;
      margin-bottom: .6rem;
    }

    .stopwatch {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .6rem;
      margin-top: .6rem;
      padding: .8rem;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .time-display {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      min-width: 90px;
    }

    button {
      padding: 10px 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #bbb;
      background: #f0f0f0;
    }

    button.primary {
      background: #d0eaff;
      border-color: #8bbfe8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    button.secondary {
      background: #f0f0f0;
    }

    .nav-buttons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .nav-buttons .right {
      margin-left: auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: .7rem;
    }

    .mini-grid {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: .6rem;
    }

    .mini-grid th,
    .mini-grid td {
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding: .5rem;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .mini-grid th:first-child,
    .mini-grid td:first-child {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .mini-grid input {
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }

    #reportBox {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #bbb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1rem;
      white-space: pre-line;
    }

    .report-section {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .report-section:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .report-section h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: .4rem;
    }

    .footer-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>Geriatrie Screening</h1>
  <p class="muted">Mehrstufiges Screening mit Patient:innen-Fragen, Vor-Ort-Testung und Abschlussreport.</p>

  <div class="stepper" id="stepper">
    <div class="step-pill active">1 Angaben</div>
    <div class="step-pill">2 Fragen</div>
    <div class="step-pill">3 Testung</div>
    <div class="step-pill">4 Mini-BESTest</div>
    <div class="step-pill">5 Report</div>
  </div>

  <!-- SEITE 1 -->
  <section class="page active" id="page0">
    <h2>1. Angaben</h2>
    <p>Diese Angaben werden von der Administration oder Therapeut:in eingetragen.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="form-grid two">
        <div>
          <label for="firstName">Vorname</label>
          <input type="text" id="firstName" autocomplete="given-name">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="lastName">Nachname</label>
          <input type="text" id="lastName" autocomplete="family-name">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="birthDate">Geburtsdatum</label>
          <input type="date" id="birthDate">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="screeningDate">Datum Screening</label>
          <input type="date" id="screeningDate">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEITE 2 -->
  <section class="page" id="page1">
    <h2>2. Patient:innen-Fragen</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>HADS-4</h3>
      <p class="muted">Die konkrete Formulierung der vier HADS-4-Fragen kann hier bei Bedarf angepasst werden.</p>

      <div id="hadsContainer"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Körperliche Aktivität</h3>

      <div class="form-grid two">
        <div>
          <label for="activeDays">An wie vielen Tagen pro Woche sind Sie körperlich aktiv?</label>
          <p class="muted">Mindestens mässig ins Schwitzen oder ausser Atem kommen, z. B. zügiges Gehen, Velofahren, Sport.</p>
          <input type="number" id="activeDays" min="0" max="7" step="1" placeholder="0–7 Tage">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="activeMinutes">Wie viele Minuten sind Sie an einem solchen Tag aktiv?</label>
          <input type="number" id="activeMinutes" min="0" step="1" placeholder="Minuten pro aktivem Tag">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Sturzfragen</h3>

      <div class="question-block">
        <div class="question-title">Sind Sie in den letzten 12 Monaten gestürzt?</div>
        <div class="radio-row">
          <label><input type="radio" name="fall12m" value="Ja"> Ja</label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="fall12m" value="Nein"> Nein</label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question-block">
        <div class="question-title">Fühlen Sie sich beim Gehen oder Stehen unsicher?</div>
        <div class="radio-row">
          <label><input type="radio" name="unsteady" value="Ja"> Ja</label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="unsteady" value="Nein"> Nein</label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question-block">
        <div class="question-title">Haben Sie Angst zu stürzen?</div>
        <div class="radio-row">
          <label><input type="radio" name="fearFall" value="Ja"> Ja</label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="fearFall" value="Nein"> Nein</label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEITE 3 -->
  <section class="page" id="page2">
    <h2>3. Testung vor Ort</h2>
    <p class="muted">Die Werte werden durch die Therapeut:in eingetragen. Die Stoppuhr kann für Gehgeschwindigkeit und 5x Sit-Stand verwendet werden.</p>

    <div class="test-card">
      <div class="test-title">Gehgeschwindigkeit</div>

      <div class="form-grid three">
        <div>
          <label for="gaitDistance">Strecke</label>
          <select id="gaitDistance">
            <option value="4">4 m</option>
            <option value="6">6 m</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="gaitTime">Zeit in Sekunden</label>
          <input type="number" id="gaitTime" min="0" step="0.01" placeholder="z. B. 5.20">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="gaitSpeed">Gehgeschwindigkeit m/s</label>
          <input type="text" id="gaitSpeed" readonly placeholder="automatisch">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stopwatch">
        <div class="time-display" id="timerDisplay">0.00 s</div>
        <button type="button" onclick="startTimer()">Start</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="stopTimer()">Stopp</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="resetTimer()">Reset</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="useTimerFor('gaitTime')">Zeit übernehmen</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="test-card">
      <div class="test-title">5x Sit-Stand</div>

      <div class="form-grid two">
        <div>
          <label for="sitStandTime">Zeit in Sekunden</label>
          <input type="number" id="sitStandTime" min="0" step="0.01" placeholder="z. B. 14.80">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="sitStandNote">Bemerkung</label>
          <input type="text" id="sitStandNote" placeholder="z. B. Armlehne benutzt / nicht möglich">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stopwatch">
        <div class="time-display" id="timerDisplay2">0.00 s</div>
        <button type="button" onclick="startTimer()">Start</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="stopTimer()">Stopp</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="resetTimer()">Reset</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="useTimerFor('sitStandTime')">Zeit übernehmen</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="test-card">
      <div class="test-title">Griffkraft</div>

      <div class="form-grid three">
        <div>
          <label for="gripLeft">Links kg</label>
          <input type="number" id="gripLeft" min="0" step="0.1" placeholder="kg">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="gripRight">Rechts kg</label>
          <input type="number" id="gripRight" min="0" step="0.1" placeholder="kg">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="gripBest">Bester Wert kg</label>
          <input type="number" id="gripBest" min="0" step="0.1" placeholder="optional">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEITE 4 -->
  <section class="page" id="page3">
    <h2>4. Mini-BESTest</h2>
    <p class="muted">Mini-BESTest direkt durchführen. Kein PDF-Export auf dieser Seite; die Resultate erscheinen im Gesamtreport.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <table class="mini-grid">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Item</th>
            <th>0</th>
            <th>1</th>
            <th>2</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="miniBestBody"></tbody>
      </table>

      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <strong>Mini-BESTest Score:</strong>
        <span id="miniBestScore">0 / 28</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Transfer Boden → Stand</h3>

      <div class="form-grid two">
        <div>
          <label for="floorTransfer">Durchführung</label>
          <select id="floorTransfer">
            <option value="">Bitte auswählen</option>
            <option value="selbstständig möglich">Selbstständig möglich</option>
            <option value="mit Hilfe möglich">Mit Hilfe möglich</option>
            <option value="nicht möglich">Nicht möglich</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="floorTransferTime">Zeit optional in Sekunden</label>
          <input type="number" id="floorTransferTime" min="0" step="0.01" placeholder="optional">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEITE 5 -->
  <section class="page" id="page4">
    <h2>5. Report</h2>
    <p class="muted">Zusammenfassung aller eingegebenen Werte ohne Interpretation.</p>

    <div id="reportBox"></div>

    <button type="button" class="primary" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Drucken / als PDF speichern</button>
  </section>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <button type="button" class="secondary" onclick="goBackPage()">⬅️ Zurück</button>

    <div class="right">
      <button type="button" class="secondary" onclick="window.location.href='index.html'">🏠 Hauptseite</button>
      <button type="button" class="primary" onclick="goNextPage()" id="nextBtn">Weiter ➡️</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    let currentPage = 0;
    const totalPages = 5;

    const hadsItems = [
      "HADS-4 Frage 1",
      "HADS-4 Frage 2",
      "HADS-4 Frage 3",
      "HADS-4 Frage 4"
    ];

    const miniBestItems = [
      "1. Sitz zu Stand",
      "2. Auf Zehenspitzen stehen",
      "3. Einbeinstand",
      "4. Kompensatorischer Schritt vorwärts",
      "5. Kompensatorischer Schritt rückwärts",
      "6. Kompensatorischer Schritt seitwärts",
      "7. Stand mit geschlossenen Augen auf Schaumstoff",
      "8. Stand auf schräger Ebene mit geschlossenen Augen",
      "9. Änderung der Gehgeschwindigkeit",
      "10. Gehen mit Kopfdrehungen",
      "11. Gehen mit Drehung um 180°",
      "12. Über Hindernis steigen",
      "13. Timed Up and Go",
      "14. Timed Up and Go mit Dual Task"
    ];

    let timerInterval = null;
    let timerStart = 0;
    let elapsed = 0;

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      setToday();
      renderHADS();
      renderMiniBest();
      updatePage();
      setupAutoCalculations();
    });

    function setToday() {
      const today = new Date().toISOString().split("T")[0];
      document.getElementById("screeningDate").value = today;
    }

    function renderHADS() {
      const container = document.getElementById("hadsContainer");
      container.innerHTML = "";

      hadsItems.forEach((text, index) => {
        const q = index + 1;
        container.innerHTML += `
          <div class="question-block">
            <div class="question-title">${text}</div>
            <div class="radio-row">
              <label><input type="radio" name="hads${q}" value="0"> 0</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="hads${q}" value="1"> 1</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="hads${q}" value="2"> 2</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="hads${q}" value="3"> 3</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        `;
      });
    }

    function renderMiniBest() {
      const body = document.getElementById("miniBestBody");
      body.innerHTML = "";

      miniBestItems.forEach((item, index) => {
        const q = index + 1;
        body.innerHTML += `
          <tr>
            <td>${item}</td>
            <td><input type="radio" name="mini${q}" value="0" onchange="calculateMiniBest()"></td>
            <td><input type="radio" name="mini${q}" value="1" onchange="calculateMiniBest()"></td>
            <td><input type="radio" name="mini${q}" value="2" onchange="calculateMiniBest()"></td>
          </tr>
        `;
      });
    }

    function setupAutoCalculations() {
      document.getElementById("gaitTime").addEventListener("input", calculateGaitSpeed);
      document.getElementById("gaitDistance").addEventListener("change", calculateGaitSpeed);
    }

    function updatePage() {
      document.querySelectorAll(".page").forEach((page, index) => {
        page.classList.toggle("active", index === currentPage);
      });

      document.querySelectorAll(".step-pill").forEach((pill, index) => {
        pill.classList.toggle("active", index === currentPage);
      });

      document.getElementById("nextBtn").textContent = currentPage === totalPages - 1 ? "Report aktualisieren" : "Weiter ➡️";

      if (currentPage === totalPages - 1) {
        generateReport();
      }

      window.scrollTo(0, 0);
    }

    function goNextPage() {
      if (currentPage < totalPages - 1) {
        currentPage++;
        updatePage();
      } else {
        generateReport();
      }
    }

    function goBackPage() {
      if (currentPage > 0) {
        currentPage--;
        updatePage();
      } else {
        window.location.href = "index.html";
      }
    }

    function startTimer() {
      if (timerInterval) return;
      timerStart = Date.now() - elapsed;
      timerInterval = setInterval(updateTimerDisplay, 20);
    }

    function stopTimer() {
      if (!timerInterval) return;
      clearInterval(timerInterval);
      timerInterval = null;
      elapsed = Date.now() - timerStart;
      updateTimerDisplay();
    }

    function resetTimer() {
      clearInterval(timerInterval);
      timerInterval = null;
      elapsed = 0;
      updateTimerDisplay();
    }

    function updateTimerDisplay() {
      if (timerInterval) elapsed = Date.now() - timerStart;
      const seconds = (elapsed / 1000).toFixed(2);
      document.getElementById("timerDisplay").textContent = `${seconds} s`;
      document.getElementById("timerDisplay2").textContent = `${seconds} s`;
    }

    function useTimerFor(inputId) {
      const seconds = (elapsed / 1000).toFixed(2);
      document.getElementById(inputId).value = seconds;
      if (inputId === "gaitTime") calculateGaitSpeed();
    }

    function calculateGaitSpeed() {
      const distance = Number(document.getElementById("gaitDistance").value);
      const time = Number(document.getElementById("gaitTime").value);
      const output = document.getElementById("gaitSpeed");

      if (!distance || !time) {
        output.value = "";
        return;
      }

      output.value = (distance / time).toFixed(2);
    }

    function calculateMiniBest() {
      let total = 0;

      for (let i = 1; i <= 14; i++) {
        const selected = document.querySelector(`input[name="mini${i}"]:checked`);
        if (selected) total += Number(selected.value);
      }

      document.getElementById("miniBestScore").textContent = `${total} / 28`;
      return total;
    }

    function radioValue(name) {
      const selected = document.querySelector(`input[name="${name}"]:checked`);
      return selected ? selected.value : "nicht beantwortet";
    }

    function inputValue(id) {
      const el = document.getElementById(id);
      return el && el.value ? el.value : "nicht eingetragen";
    }

    function calculateHADS() {
      let total = 0;
      let answered = 0;

      for (let i = 1; i <= 4; i++) {
        const selected = document.querySelector(`input[name="hads${i}"]:checked`);
        if (selected) {
          total += Number(selected.value);
          answered++;
        }
      }

      return { total, answered };
    }

    function generateReport() {
      calculateGaitSpeed();
      const hads = calculateHADS();
      const miniBestTotal = calculateMiniBest();

      const firstName = inputValue("firstName");
      const lastName = inputValue("lastName");
      const birthDate = inputValue("birthDate");
      const screeningDate = inputValue("screeningDate");

      const activeDays = inputValue("activeDays");
      const activeMinutes = inputValue("activeMinutes");

      const gaitDistance = inputValue("gaitDistance");
      const gaitTime = inputValue("gaitTime");
      const gaitSpeed = inputValue("gaitSpeed");

      const sitStandTime = inputValue("sitStandTime");
      const sitStandNote = inputValue("sitStandNote");

      const gripLeft = inputValue("gripLeft");
      const gripRight = inputValue("gripRight");
      const gripBest = inputValue("gripBest");

      const floorTransfer = inputValue("floorTransfer");
      const floorTransferTime = inputValue("floorTransferTime");

      document.getElementById("reportBox").innerHTML = `
        <div class="report-section">
          <h3>Patient:in</h3>
          <p><strong>Name:</strong> ${firstName} ${lastName}<br>
          <strong>Geburtsdatum:</strong> ${birthDate}<br>
          <strong>Screening-Datum:</strong> ${screeningDate}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-section">
          <h3>HADS-4</h3>
          <p><strong>Score:</strong> ${hads.total} / 12<br>
          <strong>Beantwortete Fragen:</strong> ${hads.answered} / 4</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-section">
          <h3>Körperliche Aktivität</h3>
          <p><strong>Tage pro Woche:</strong> ${activeDays}<br>
          <strong>Minuten pro aktivem Tag:</strong> ${activeMinutes}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-section">
          <h3>Sturzfragen</h3>
          <p><strong>Sturz in den letzten 12 Monaten:</strong> ${radioValue("fall12m")}<br>
          <strong>Unsicherheit beim Gehen oder Stehen:</strong> ${radioValue("unsteady")}<br>
          <strong>Angst zu stürzen:</strong> ${radioValue("fearFall")}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-section">
          <h3>Vor-Ort-Testung</h3>
          <p><strong>Gehgeschwindigkeit:</strong> ${gaitDistance} m in ${gaitTime} s = ${gaitSpeed} m/s<br>
          <strong>5x Sit-Stand:</strong> ${sitStandTime} s<br>
          <strong>Bemerkung 5x Sit-Stand:</strong> ${sitStandNote}<br>
          <strong>Griffkraft links:</strong> ${gripLeft} kg<br>
          <strong>Griffkraft rechts:</strong> ${gripRight} kg<br>
          <strong>Griffkraft bester Wert:</strong> ${gripBest} kg</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-section">
          <h3>Mini-BESTest</h3>
          <p><strong>Score:</strong> ${miniBestTotal} / 28</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-section">
          <h3>Transfer Boden → Stand</h3>
          <p><strong>Durchführung:</strong> ${floorTransfer}<br>
          <strong>Zeit:</strong> ${floorTransferTime} s</p>
        </div>
      `;
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
